OL,11,     Gchange their minds?
OL,12,G1750FCome Dine with Me
OL,13,     GOutspoken hairdresser Patrick
OL,14,     Gserves beef Wellington, but guest
OL,15,     GSharon finds him annoying.
OL,16,G1825FFour in a Bed
OL,17,     GDo the B&Bers like to be beside
OL,18,     Gthe seaside? First host Andy
