OL,4,G1955FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GTensions are already bubbling
OL,6,     Gaway between the B&Bers before
OL,7,     Gthey've even arrived at Ying and
OL,8,     GJean's Castle Inn, in Powys. But
OL,9,     Gthe hosts have the answer to
OL,10,     Grestore harmony: pies.
OL,11,G2025FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's payment day. Nowhere else
OL,13,     Gwill you find such consternation
OL,14,     Gabout whether a double bed is
OL,15,     Greally a double bed if it's two
OL,16,     Gsingle beds pushed together.
OL,17,     GWho's won?
